  #project-pandafan-content
    hr
    .container-fluid
        .container.project-section.overview
            .row.section-title
                .col-md-12.text-center
                    h3 Overview
            .row.section-content
                .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
                    p PandaFan is an online VPN service provider that helps users in mainland China bypass the Great Fire Wall and access banned sites freely. As UX Designer, I am contracted to redesign their user interface to support more features and improve usability.

    hr
