        .container.project-section.solution
            .row.section-title
                    .col-md-12.text-center
                        h3 Solution
                .row.section-content
                    .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
                        p I redesigned the dashboard interface and developed the web template using Foundation. The web template adopts responsive design.
                        p Following changes has been made compare to the old version.

