    hr
    .container-fluid
      .container.project-section.process
        .row.section-title
                .col-md-12.text-center
                    h3 Process
            .row.section-content
                .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
                    .row
                        .col-md-6.process-content-wrapper
                            .process-content-container
                                h4 Research Current Product
                                p The focus of the project is to improve usability. Therefore, I started the process with usability test of the old version. Existing problems in usability includes:
                                ul
                                    li User do not know where to seek help
                                    li There are too many pop-overs that potentially confuses user
                                    li Current design does not reflect the new feature hierarchy

                        .col-md-6
                            img(src="/images/pandafan-process-1.svg")
                    
                    .row
                        
                        .col-md-6.process-content-wrapper
                            .process-content-container
                                h4 Contextual Inquiry & User Stories
                                p Based on usability test, I proposed various user stories and also conducted contextual inquiry 
                        .col-md-6
                            img(src="/images/pandafan-process-2.svg")
                    
                    .row
                        
                        .col-md-6.process-content-wrapper
                            .process-content-container
                                h4 Wireframing
                                p A wireframe model was then made for another round of user testing. Users are asked to go through the tasks.
                        .col-md-6
                            img(src="/images/pandafan-process-3.svg")
                    
                    .row
                        .col-md-6.process-content-wrapper
                            .process-content-container
                                h4 High Fidelity Design
                                p A high fidelity design was created using Illustrator based on the feedback gathered from user testing
                        .col-md-6
                            img(src="/images/pandafan-process-4.svg")
                        
                    .row
                        .col-md-6.process-content-wrapper
                            .process-content-container
                                h4 Prototyping
                                p Finally, I turn the design into code and hand it over to back-end engineer for back-end integration.
                        .col-md-6
                            img(src="/images/pandafan-process-5.svg")
                        
                    
                        

                    
